{
  "texts": [
    "However, to the best of our knowledge, no method has adopted the strategy of first identifying nonsensical concepts and then reconstructing implicit knowledge to prompt LLMs for commonsense explanation generation.",
    "Knowledge-enhanced text generationKnowledge-enhanced text generation systems [36][37][38] leverage external knowledge sources to augment the language generation process, resulting in outputs that exhibit a deeper understanding of the context and subject matter.",
    "Previous research mainly focuses on question answering [39,40], summarization [41,42], conversation systems [42,43] and other fields.",
    "One of the most significant challenges in knowledge-enhanced text generation is to obtain valuable and relevant knowledge from different sources.",
    "This challenge involves extracting and integrating meaningful knowledge from various information sources to enable more accurate and enriched expression of content during the text generation process."
  ]
}